Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any human whose name is written in this notebook shall... {\alpha&HFF&}die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any human whose name is written in this notebook shall... die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! {\alpha&HFF&}Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, {\alpha&HFF&}let's see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}don't read this line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note... {\alpha&HFF&}It's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note... It's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume that a human who has used the Death Note can go to Heaven or Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to let the world know of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That there is someone who can, and will, pass righteous judgement!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll become... {\alpha&HFF&}the God of my new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll become... the God of my new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:43.02,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(361,347)}Showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was over-flooded with satisfaction and zealous, then finally his dream came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:49.70,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never tell what he was thinking, so I had to finish with him
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.98,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? So, after that, what happened with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun? {\alpha&HFF&}Could you please translate the previous passage into Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun? Could you please translate the previous passage into Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having finally made his dream a reality, he was overwhelmed by the sense of his own achievement and the joy it brought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. {\alpha&HFF&}A perfect translation, but I'd expect nothing less from you, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. A perfect translation, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'd expect nothing less from you, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. A perfect translation, but I'd expect nothing less from you, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave it here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I glad that that's finally over. {\alpha&HFF&}This "school" thing really bores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I glad that that's finally over. This "school" thing really bores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me. {\alpha&HFF&}Other people can hear my voice, unlike yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me. Other people can hear my voice, unlike yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light! We're all gonna head to th--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I've got things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have "things" to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just gonna go home like always?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? {\alpha&HFF&}I do have "things" to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I do have "things" to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very important things...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada is suspected of stabbing a fellow employee in the stomach at a restaurant in Kabukichi, Shinjuku, yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The knife was from the restaurant, and was roughly twelve inches long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... {\alpha&HFF&}Hey, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Hey, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all the effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I can't afford to waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time that I have to write names in the notebook is limited from when I come home and until I go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important that I maintain my grades, so I can't sleep in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't neglect my studies at home or cram school either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, losing sleep will affect my health and my mental capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm serious about changing the world into a purer place, {\alpha&HFF&}no matter how much time I have, it will never be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm serious about changing the world into a purer place, no matter how much time I have, it will never be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Onii-chan, why is your door locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..It's Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help me with my homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.. Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, in Maths, we're doing quadratic equations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disturb you when you're studying, but I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Light. {\alpha&HFF&}If anyone touches that notebook in your drawer, they'll be able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Light. If anyone touches that notebook in your drawer, they'll be able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You waited until now to mention such an important detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damned Shinigami..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. {\alpha&HFF&}Anyway, which bit are you stuck on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Anyway, which bit are you stuck on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. {\alpha&HFF&}All of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. All of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:44.37,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,ICPO, or Interpol, stands for International Criminal Police Organization
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been 52 known cases in this week alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them involved heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them involved criminals that are either already in jail, or being pursued by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's safe to assume that there are still many other deaths that we are yet unaware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, the total could easily be over 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already started, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I had to take a call from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're all criminals who should have faced the death penalty sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we care?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter whether it's a criminal, death row prisoner or whatever! If you kill someone, then that's murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But surely it hasn't been confirmed as a homicide yet, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 100 criminals dying of heart attacks, coincidences like that doesn't exist! {\alpha&HFF&}It's obviously murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 100 criminals dying of heart attacks, coincidences like that doesn't exist! It's obviously murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you honestly think it's possible to commit so many murders, in different locations, almost all at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're treating this as an elaborate assassination plot that is being carried out by a large organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large organization? Then, surely the FBI or the CIA must be involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa. Let's not mess around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing we need to determine, is whether this is murder or just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the coroners have all ruled a verdict of "heart attack with no known cause".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening a police investigation into heart attacks is going to get us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, if only they'd use a knife or something, then we'd have something to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it looks like we've got no choice but to bring in "L" again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, what's "L"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'd forgotten that it's your first time here at this conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"L" is someone whose real name and whereabouts are unknown. We don't even know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, he always manages to solve every single case he takes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's solved countless mysterious incidents all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the best of those hidden deep within the shadows.. {\alpha&HFF&}Our trump card. That sums him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the best of those hidden deep within the shadows.. Our trump card. That sums him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've heard that L is supposedly an extremely arrogant individual who'll only take on cases that interests him personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! We don't even have a way of contacting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L is already on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L has already begun his investigations into these incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-{\alpha&HFF&}Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one man who knows how to contact L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows his true identity either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, quiet please. {\alpha&HFF&}L will now speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, quiet please. L will now speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings to all of you at the ICPO.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the secrecy? {\alpha&HFF&}What're you planning to do in this isolated place, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the secrecy? What're you planning to do in this isolated place, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who touches the Death Note can see you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't risk keeping such a dangerous article in a regular place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, I'd been thinking that even if by chance this notebook was seen by my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could end the matter by saying I was "taking records of incidents to study for when I become a detective".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm walking a really thin line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one mistake.. {\alpha&HFF&}and I might have to kill off one of my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one mistake.. and I might have to kill off one of my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difficulty of this case is on a scale that I've never experienced before.. {\alpha&HFF&}and, it's an atrocious murder case that I will never forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difficulty of this case is on a scale that I've never experienced before.. and, {\alpha&HFF&}it's an atrocious murder case that I will never forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difficulty of this case is on a scale that I've never experienced before.. and, it's an atrocious murder case that I will never forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to solve this case, I would like to have everyone in the ICPO,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, the organizations you all represent throughout the world, make the decision to lend their full support to me in this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, {\alpha&HFF&}I will require special cooperation from the Japanese police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, I will require special cooperation from the Japanese police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Why Japan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why Japan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether there's one or more culprits involved, {\alpha&HFF&}the probability of them being Japanese is extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether there's one or more culprits involved, the probability of them being Japanese is extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're not Japanese, it's likely that they are in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you basing this theory on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to be able to show you soon.. when I go head-to-head with the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head-to-head?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'd like the investigation headquarters to be based in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was easier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you've managed to hide the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.. {\alpha&HFF&}in this drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.. in this drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem to be particularly hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that key a bit of a give-away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the whole point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better that it is noticeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just a normal diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing that most people will have their curiosity satisfied by finding this inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the real key.. {\alpha&HFF&}is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the real key.. is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just an everyday item you'd expect to find on any desk.. The center of a ball-point pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}On closer examination, you'll find a small hole in the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. On closer examination, you'll find a small hole in the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pen's center is inserted into the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A fake base, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, combined with the diary, means that it'll probably be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if someone does figure out that there's a fake base, {\alpha&HFF&}there's no way they could get their hands on this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if someone does figure out that there's a fake base, there's no way they could get their hands on this notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, {\alpha&HFF&}this ball-point pen acts as an insulator preventing the flow of electricity round this circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, this ball-point pen acts as an insulator preventing the flow of electricity round this circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the fake base is returned, the rubber stops the flow of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if someone tries to force the fake base open, {\alpha&HFF&}the circuit will connect and the gasoline in this thin plastic bag will instantly incinerate the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if someone tries to force the fake base open, the circuit will connect and the gasoline in this thin plastic bag will instantly incinerate the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the evidence will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am asked about this I'll just tell them, "I didn't want anyone to read my diary."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a believable excuse. After all, it's human nature to hide your own diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that the main problem humans have with a Death Note is how to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you're probably the first person to have given it this much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that is a pretty risky setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One mistake and you could end up in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risk? {\alpha&HFF&}Sometimes you say some funny things, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risk? Sometimes you say some funny things, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole thing has been a risk from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the minute I found the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, this doesn't even qualify as a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, it actually protects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, a death sentence? Or a small house fire? Which do you think is better?
Comment: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night in a prison in western Tokyo, Kurotsukayama Naoki, aged 32, previously convicted for armed robbery, has been reported to have died of a sudden heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sudden phenomenon of inmates dying from heart attacks appears to be continuing..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is incredible! Criminals are dropping like flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda scary, but at the same time, it's exhilarating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means that we can't risk doing anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you reckon the police are probably behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police don't have that kind of power! {\alpha&HFF&}Don't you know who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police don't have that kind of power! Don't you know who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Kira" who's behind this. "Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder who'll be next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.51,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira, kill them all."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Websites like this have already started to emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The legend of Kira - Our saviour"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira taken from the english word "Killer".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't really say that I appreciate that too much, {\alpha&HFF&}but I guess that's what the world now knows me as.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't really say that I appreciate that too much, but I guess that's what the world now knows me as.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get so many sites like this just from a mere search on the word "kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the papers and on TV, it's still not been reported as anything but "a succession of strange deaths amongst the criminals".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}the people of this world are already starting to become aware that there's someone out there judging them, in the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the people of this world are already starting to become aware that there's someone out there judging them, in the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are like that, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unlikely, but if anyone asked if killing bad people was wrong in school, {\alpha&HFF&}people would get on their moral high horse, saying "That's wrong!".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unlikely, but if anyone asked if killing bad people was wrong in school, people would get on their moral high horse, saying {\alpha&HFF&}"That's wrong!".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unlikely, but if anyone asked if killing bad people was wrong in school, people would get on their moral high horse, saying "That's wrong!".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that is the correct answer to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans will always seek to maintain appearances in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is what they're really thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're too scared to support me publicly, {\alpha&HFF&}they can hide behind the anonymity of the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're too scared to support me publicly, they can hide behind the anonymity of the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.84,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\pos(348,367)}KIRA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Support for "Kira" is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have to say it, {\alpha&HFF&}because they already know, someone is erasing the wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have to say it, because they already know, {\alpha&HFF&}someone is erasing the wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have to say it, because they already know, someone is erasing the wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The innocent are screaming inside; "Go for it Kira!", while those who are guilty, run and hide in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is progressing exactly as I'd planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.49,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,154)}Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.49,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(361,271)}The scheduled program
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.49,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,395)}will be interrupted \Nfor a special broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologies for the interruption, but we now bring you a live worldwide broadcast from the ICPO, Interpol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interpol?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're ready to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only person who can control the entire world's police forces, {\alpha&HFF&}Lind L. Tailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only person who can control the entire world's police forces, Lind L. Tailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I go by the code name.. {\alpha&HFF&}"L".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I go by the code name.. "L".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so it begins..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't understand. He's never shown his face before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it means he's taking this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, L... {\alpha&HFF&}We've followed every single one of your orders, now it's time for you to fulfill those promises you made at the ICPO conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, L... We've followed every single one of your orders, {\alpha&HFF&}now it's time for you to fulfill those promises you made at the ICPO conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, L... We've followed every single one of your orders, now it's time for you to fulfill those promises you made at the ICPO conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This successive murdering of criminals is unforgivable, {\alpha&HFF&}and must not go unpunished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This successive murdering of criminals is unforgivable, and must not go unpunished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee I will find and catch the ring leader, or "Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he'll guarantee that he'll catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way he can catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! There's no way he can catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Death Note!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they don't find it, what proof will they have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching me is impossible! {\alpha&HFF&}Absolutely impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching me is impossible! Absolutely impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd already anticipated that the police would get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, I can guess what your motivation might be, {\alpha&HFF&}but what you're doing is evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, I can guess what your motivation might be, but what you're doing is {\alpha&HFF&}evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, I can guess what your motivation might be, but what you're doing is evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the evil one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am justice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I save the weak from evil {\alpha&HFF&}and will become the God of a world that everyone desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I save the weak from evil and will become the God of a world that everyone desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who try to cross God are the true evil ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that you're this stupid, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could have been fun, {\alpha&HFF&}if you'd been a little smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could have been fun, if you'd been a little smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show the world what happens when you cross me, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... {\alpha&HFF&}Four.. Three.. Two.. One..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... Four.. {\alpha&HFF&}Three.. Two.. One..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... Four.. Three.. {\alpha&HFF&}Two.. One..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... Four.. Three.. Two.. {\alpha&HFF&}One..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds... Four.. Three.. Two.. One..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Now, what do you have to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tested it just in case, {\alpha&HFF&}but I never thought it could actually be true..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tested it just in case, but I never thought it could actually be true..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}it seems you can kill people without having to be there in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, it seems you can kill people without having to be there in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to believe this if I hadn't just witnessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely, Kira; {\alpha&HFF&}if you did indeed kill the "Lind L. Tailor" on screen, I can tell you that he was in fact a criminal that was due to be put to death today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely, Kira; if you did indeed kill the "Lind L. Tailor" on screen, {\alpha&HFF&}I can tell you that he was in fact a criminal that was due to be put to death today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely, Kira; if you did indeed kill the "Lind L. Tailor" on screen, I can tell you that he was in fact a criminal that was due to be put to death today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have heard of him on the news or through the Internet. {\alpha&HFF&}He was a criminal that was captured by the police in absolute secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have heard of him on the news or through the Internet. He was a criminal that was captured by the police in absolute secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like not even you have information on these kinds of killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely got ya this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for L, he certainly does exist, as my own persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, {\alpha&HFF&}try and kill me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, try and kill me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&HFF&}You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill yourself, L?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taunting Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's L vs. Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it seems you can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there are certain people you can't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a reward, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll tell you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a reward, I'll tell you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lied about this being a live worldwide broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This announcement is currently only being broadcast across the Kanto region of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning to broadcast it at different times, across different regions, but it seems that there is no longer any need for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in Kanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this guy, L, is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first killing was overlooked by the police as it was such a small incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, your first victim was in fact the phantom killer in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While the other high profile criminals were dying of heart attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this was the one incident that stuck out as being quite a heavy punishment for a relatively low profile crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, {\alpha&HFF&}that incident was only reported within Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, that incident was only reported within Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.20,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35.59322\frz24\pos(359,282)}Otoharada Kurou
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just those pieces of information were enough for me to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that you are in Japan, {\alpha&HFF&}and that that criminal was your first "experiment".
